'''2018年环西自行车赛'''是第73届[[环西自行车赛|环西自行车赛]]，于2018年8月25日至9月16日进行，此次比赛是2018年UCI世界巡回赛的其中一站比赛<ref>{{cite web|url=https://movistarteam.com/en/2018-08-20/2018-vuelta-espana-lineup|title=Movistar Team announces Vuelta a España lineup|work=Movistar Team|date=2018-08-20|accessdate=2020-09-29|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180823143630/http://movistarteam.com/en/2018-08-20/2018-vuelta-espana-lineup|archivedate=2018-08-23|dead-url=no}}</ref>。比赛共分为21个赛段，起点位于[[马拉加|马拉加]]，终点位于[[马德里|马德里]]，除第19赛段途经安道尔，第20赛段在[[安道尔|安道尔]]境内进行外，其余比赛路线均在西班牙境内。<ref name="Oficial">{{cite news |url=http://www.lavuelta.com/la-vuelta/2018/us/pre-race/news/ahc/the-official-route-of-la-vuelta-2018-is-revealed-in-estepona.html |title=The official route of la Vuelta 2018 is revealed in Estepona |publisher=La Vuelta |date=2018-01-13 |accessdate=2018-01-13 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180522020333/http://www.lavuelta.com/la-vuelta/2018/us/pre-race/news/ahc/the-official-route-of-la-vuelta-2018-is-revealed-in-estepona.html |archivedate=2018-05-22 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

共有22支车队参加此次比赛，其中18支车队为世界职业车队，另外4支车队则为洲际职业车队<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.cyclingnews.com/news/vuelta-a-espana-snubs-aqua-blue-sport-in-favour-of-home-teams-wild-cards/|title=Vuelta a Espana snubs Aqua Blue Sport in favour of home teams wild cards|work=Cycling News|date=2018-04-10|accessdate=2020-09-29|archiveurl=https://archive.today/20200929132405/https://www.cyclingnews.com/news/vuelta-a-espana-snubs-aqua-blue-sport-in-favour-of-home-teams-wild-cards/|archivedate=2020-09-29}}{{cbignore}}</ref>。最终来自Mitchelton–Scott车队的[[Simon_Yates_(cyclist)|Simon Yates]]获得此次比赛的总冠军，这是他的首个三大自行车赛总冠军<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.bbc.com/sport/cycling/45540766|title=Simon Yates: British cyclist wins first Grand Tour at Vuelta a Espana|date=2018-09-16|publisher=[[BBC体育|BBC Sport]]|access-date=2018-09-16|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180917022642/https://www.bbc.com/sport/cycling/45540766|archivedate=2018-09-17|dead-url=no}}</ref>。来自快步车队的[[Enric_Mas|Enric Mas]]和来自阿斯塔纳车队的[[Miguel_Ángel_López|Miguel Ángel López]]分别获得二三名。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://as.com/ciclismo/2018/09/15/vuelta_espana/1537028221_324569.html|script-title=es:Enric Mas gana la etapa reina, sube al podio y aclara el futuro|publisher=AS|date=2018-09-15|accessdate=2020-09-29|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180915213736/https://as.com/ciclismo/2018/09/15/vuelta_espana/1537028221_324569.html|archivedate=2018-09-15|dead-url=no}}</ref>

